			Shot Homing Stars to the enemy
			"Shine of the little stars"
			'''
		DisplayName: Wand of Star Shine
	}

	TwinkleBag: {
		Tooltip: ""
		DisplayName: Treasure Bag (Twinkle)
	}

	TomeOfEclipsa: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			[c/864A0E:Created By:] [c/870D75:Zexino]
			A forbidden tome that channels the darkness of a solar eclipse.
			Launches lingering orbs that drain the essence of your foes.
			"The eclipse never truly ends."
			'''
		DisplayName: Tome Of Eclipsa
	}

	BlackwhipItem: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Inherits the unyielding wills of previous vestiges. Unleashes 3 chaotic strands of shadow energy in a wide spread.
			"Channels absolute Main Character Energy. Wraps your targets in crackling, unstable teal lightning, 
			locking them down with a gravitational Vortex effect..."
			[c/FF4500:WARNING:] Regular grappling hooks are completely disabled by this sheer alpha energy. Also, 
			the devs are not legally responsible for any severe spinal injuries. 
			Bro really crafted the entire wiki into a rope.
			'''
		DisplayName: Blackwhip
	}

	TwinkleTwinkle: {
		Tooltip:
			'''
			Summon Eyeless Stars Minion to Fight
			"The Power of the Star now in your Side"
			'''
		DisplayName: Twinkle Twinkle Staff
